QUALITY POLICY MANUAL — ISO 9001:2015 COMPLIANCE FRAMEWORK
Policy Ref: POL-002 | Version: v3.1 | Author: Quality Assurance Dept

1. QUALITY MANAGEMENT FRAMEWORK OVERVIEW
IntelliPlant AI enforces ISO 9001:2015 quality principles to ensure continuous industrial asset reliability and statutory compliance.
- Clause 6 (Planning): Risk-based maintenance scheduling and predictive RUL modeling.
- Clause 8 (Operation): Execution of work orders, inspection completion logging, and NCR escalation.
- Clause 9 (Performance Evaluation): Real-time tracking of framework compliance scores (Factory Act 98%, ISO 9001 96%, PESO 88%).
- Clause 10 (Improvement): Root cause investigation and CAPA tracking for all audit non-conformances.